    {
      "Text": "An update for pipewire is now available for openEuler-24.03-LTS-SP3",
      "Title": "Summary",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
      "Text": "is a server and user space API to deal with multimedia pipelines,contains command line utilities.\n\nSecurity Fix(es):\n\nRAOP module accepts unbounded Content-Length values and does not check the pw_array_add() return.(CVE-2026-14324)",
      "Title": "Description",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
      "Text": "An update for pipewire is now available for openEuler-24.03-LTS-SP3.\n\nopenEuler Security has rated this update as having a security impact of medium. A Common Vunlnerability Scoring System(CVSS)base score,which gives a detailed severity rating, is available for each vulnerability from the CVElink(s) in the References section.",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
      "Text": "Medium",
      "Title": "Severity",
      "Type": "General"
